'''K-15海洋导弹''' ([[梵语|梵语]]: [[Devanagari|सागरिका]]) 是一种核弹头[[潜射弹道导弹|潜射弹道导弹]]，射程为{{convert|700|km|0}}.它是{{link-en|K系列飛彈|K Missile family}}最有名气的一种，组成了印度的[[核三位一体|核三位一体]]关键的潜射一极，并给印度提供了[[离岸打击|离岸打击]]的能力<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ibnlive.com/news/india-gets-submarinebased-nuclear-missile/44268-3.html |title=India gets sub-marine missile power |publisher=Ibnlive.com |date=2007-07-07 |accessdate=2013-05-02 |archive-date=2008-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617222548/http://www.ibnlive.com/news/india-gets-submarinebased-nuclear-missile/44268-3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>它之前长期被错误报导成巡航导弹。还有人误认为是“烈火2”导弹水下型，现在比较一致的看法是它是“大地3”的水下型。在它服役前，印度海军只拥有“丹努什”式水面舰载弹道导弹。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://war.163.com/09/0807/19/5G4VNQMQ00011232.html |title="短矛"对准中国？印度K-15潜射导弹 |accessdate=2014-05-03 |archive-date=2020-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203021049/http://war.163.com/09/0807/19/5G4VNQMQ00011232.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

